{"tid":1987961,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"唔好畀人帶住走啦，關於屎渣郭偉健單嘢","createTime":"2020-04-25T00:37:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T08:42:18.000Z","uid":139319,"like":429,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"9fe1ea2c28773aca0396c3026707f7fc11d96518","tid":1987961,"uid":139319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T00:37:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">單案嘅重點係律政屎署㨂黎告條最輕嘅罪擺係區院審，而區院又係佢哋屎渣嘅自己友範圍，8~9成係屎渣藍屍...</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">呢單案最少應該係高院告條仚家剷 傷人17 - 根據 第212章《侵害人身罪條例》 第17條 ，意圖造成身體嚴重傷害而傷人 &amp; 企圖謀殺。仆佢個街，而家係告又告得輕、判又判得輕。反過來睇，告手足黃絲就搵條最重嘅黎告，判又盡量去到最盡。我真係好想香港畀人核爆!!!</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"63e2f4ad93070c962c57ae8d042fac8a4873cd9e","tid":1987961,"uid":125079,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T00:39:28.000Z","msg":"香港法治一早仆街<br />\n<br />\n依班狗官同香港人勢不兩立"},{"pid":"ae42c160aa61097f799409758eb46415c37b44e6","tid":1987961,"uid":17838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T00:40:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd5753bfa5a6f19ae20a7055856fb0e437ef6f32","tid":1987961,"uid":139319,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T00:42:33.000Z","msg":"+1/10"},{"pid":"aa0cf51c037e778a8ca18a0d89ce5093049b845c","tid":1987961,"uid":139319,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T00:43:12.000Z","msg":"邊條狗畀左負皮，同我走出黎奶屎"},{"pid":"a8d49f5e2fa157e5655af8b6ef6d67ff8f09bbaa","tid":1987961,"uid":246023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T00:43:32.000Z","msg":"警世"},{"pid":"9bb66fe7e42f32b0d99481278eb55d5f3fc903e9","tid":1987961,"uid":139319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T00:44:15.